I"T<p>Auto Drifter is a <strong>top-down 2D racing</strong> game in which the player competes against the AI in a race, drifting around corners while the car automatically accelerates. The game was made for a course as part of my <a href="https://www.aau.at/en/studien/master-game-studies-and-engineering/">Masters degree</a>, with the condition that the game had to only be played with one button. <!--more-->
I made two versions of the game, one played with one button where the player can only turn counter-clockwise, and another where the player can turn either direction using two buttons.</p>
